@startuml DS-0
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign left
skinparam maxMessageSize 180
title DS-0 : Initialisation du système\n(Health Check + démarrage architecture)

actor       "DevOps / Admin"                    as ADM
boundary    "CLI / Docker Compose"               as CLI
control     "AppLifespan\n(main.py)"             as APP
control     "MigrationRunner\n(Alembic)"         as MIG
control     "SeedScript"                         as SEED
entity      "RoleModel"                          as ROLE
entity      "UserModel"                          as USER
database    "PostgreSQL"                         as DB

== Démarrage des services ==
ADM  ->  CLI  : docker-compose up --build
CLI  ->  APP  : start FastAPI application
activate APP
APP  ->  APP  : validate_encryption_configuration()
alt ENCRYPTION_KEY manquante
    APP  --> CLI  : raise ValueError("ENCRYPTION_KEY requis")
    CLI  --> ADM  : erreur — démarrage annulé
else configuration valide
    APP  ->  MIG  : run_migrations()
    activate MIG
    MIG  ->  DB   : alembic upgrade head
    DB   --> MIG  : migrations appliquées
    MIG  --> APP  : ok
    deactivate MIG
end

opt seed initial requis
    ADM  ->  SEED : python -m app.db.seed
    activate SEED
    SEED ->  ROLE : checkOrCreate(["admin","developer","security_manager","viewer"])
    activate ROLE
    ROLE ->  DB   : SELECT / INSERT INTO roles
    DB   --> ROLE : roles
    ROLE --> SEED : ok
    deactivate ROLE
    SEED ->  USER : checkOrCreate(primaryAdmin)
    activate USER
    USER ->  DB   : SELECT / INSERT INTO users
    DB   --> USER : user
    USER --> SEED : ok
    deactivate USER
    SEED --> ADM  : seed terminé
    deactivate SEED
end

== Health Check ==
ADM  ->  CLI  : GET /api/health
CLI  ->  APP  : handleHealthCheck(): HealthResponse
APP  ->  DB   : ping(): bool
DB   --> APP  : pong
APP  --> CLI  : 200 { status:"ok", db:"connected", version:"x.y.z" }
CLI  --> ADM  : système opérationnel
deactivate APP

@enduml
